00:11:30.831 --> 00:11:33.913
"Jadi, aku menyerah."

00:11:34.622 --> 00:11:36.664
'Saya juga tidak mencintai Devyani'

00:11:38.497 --> 00:11:40.912
'atau ingin menikahinya.'

00:11:54.455 --> 00:11:55.580
'Di Sini'

00:11:56.413 --> 00:11:59.747
'kamu juga jangan pernah
menyusahkanku lagi.'

00:12:13.664 --> 00:12:14.872
Devi.  - Devi.

00:12:15.955 --> 00:12:17.288
Pulkit.

